    "body": "Thanks for bringing it up, I don't expect `transifex-migrate-resource.py` to ever work again, for two reasons:\r\n- As @hebasto mentions, XLIFF probably requires a different treatment.\r\n- The Transifex API version used by the script (v2) is deprecated and will be removed (Starting [April 7th, 2022](https://docs.transifex.com/api/introduction). apparently). But it was already working less well for recent releases.\r\n\r\nSo if it can be replaced by something Transifex provides themselves that would be nice.",
